house_details.description: Fantastic two-story David Weekley home w/ 4BR/3.5BA/3Car & extraordinary 100' wide front lot w/ abundant backyard space & garden.  The tour begins at the extended foyer, anchored by a large Study w/ double French doors & formal Dining room. The spacious Family room opens to the Kitchen & features soaring ceilings to the 2nd level. The fabulous Kitchen is a natural gathering spot, featuring an oversized dine-in Island, abundant maple cabinets, updated stainless appliances & adjoining Breakfast room. The Primary Bedroom enjoys ample natural light, a spacious private bath & walk-in closet w/ built-in shelving.  Located upstairs is a large Game Room w/ an open view of the downstairs, three additional Bedrooms & two Full Baths.  Wood & tile flooring throughout main living areas. Fresh interior paint & new carpet in Bedrooms, Game Room & stairs.  Water softener, security cameras & recently purchased storage shed convey with home.
